{"arkId":"cl010096651","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010096651","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Aigui\u00e8re : Enl\u00e8vement de D\u00e9janire d\u0027apr\u00e8s Giambologna","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Aigui\u00e8re : Enl\u00e8vement de D\u00e9janire d\u0027apr\u00e8s Giambologna"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1615","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 527 - Adolphe Rothschild, Vitrine 3","room":"Salle 527, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1615,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"D\u00e9but du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Kramer, Tobias","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Attribu\u00e9 \u00e0","dates":[{"date":"1582","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1634","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"attribution","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q36006152"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MR 486","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"D 868","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"MV 425","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"statuette ; orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le sujet de ce groupe, fondu, cisel\u00e9 et partiellement dor\u00e9, est inspir\u00e9 des M\u00e9tamorphoses d\u0027Ovide. Le centaure Nessus est repr\u00e9sent\u00e9 au moment o\u00f9 il saisie D\u00e9janire sur son dos et l\u0027enl\u00e8ve. L\u0027orf\u00e8vre prend directement mod\u00e8le sur un bronze de Giambologna pour ex\u00e9cuter ce groupe. Ce dernier a perdu son socle et ainsi ses poin\u00e7ons. Un bassin devai